page.title: 17Birds in Craignish area.
page.content: Observed in N.W. section of block:- Black-backed Gull (Great & Lesser), Blackbird, Black Guillemot, Bramble Finch, Bullfinch, Bunting (Reed & Yellow), Buzzard (& Rough-legged), Chaffinch, Chiff-chaff,Coal (& Blue & Great) Titmouse,Common Sandpiper/Snipe /Tern, Coot, Crow (Carrion & Hooded), Cuckoo, Curlew (& C.Sandpiper),Dipper, Ring Dove,Duck (Eider & Sheld),Dunlin, Fieldfare,Flycatcher (Pied & Spotted), Goldcrest, Goldeneye, Goldfinch, Goose (Grey Lag & Pink-footed),Grebe(Little) Greenfinch, Green Plover, Greenshank, Gull(Black-headed & Common & Herring), Hen Harrier, Hawfinch, Hawk (Kestrel & Sparrow),Hedge(& House)Sparrow, Heron, House Martin, Jackdaw,Kestrel, Linnet, Long-tailed Titmouse,Mallard,Merganser Merlin, Mistle Thrush,Mute Swan, Short -eared Owl, Oyster Catcher, Pheasant, Pied Wagtail,Pipit(Rock & Water)(CONT)
